3119650912-11-11 31196509Tangled Up In Blue p1 Mt Tibrogargan / Summit Caves  31196509 31196509Sport climbing doesn't get much more adventurous than this. Solo 15m on broken rock to first bolt above the void. Fearfully edge out into space to mercifully clip a second bolt and feel like you might not die if you fall. Romp up sharp jug-horns, hoping beyond hope your rope doesn't get sliced as it weaves around them. Get your breath back by hanging upside down beneath the crux. Hump and pinch for all you're worth to breach the crux, clip the anchor; now consider how you'll clean the thing. **31196509
